      "content": "\"letting go\"... i dont know. sounds so much easier said than done when you're still stuck in this shell of a person. people look at me and they don't see a person anymore, they just see a mistake. a huge, public mistake. it feels like the version of me that actually mattered died a long time ago. like there's just no path back from this level of disgrace.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
